      "Added individual_provider terms (اكتب لكم, etc.) for ad detection",
      "Added technical_problem_terms to reduce academic weight when 'حل' appears with tech context",
      "Added academic_object_weight config for phrase vs single word",
      "English academic terms without Arabic verb now implicitly weighted lower",
      "Hard rules now only add boost, never bypass pipeline"
    ]
